ents to be in control of where they want to go  for an extra personal touch we can even personalise gift cards and carriers to reflect your company’s brandingthe card gives access to over  travel companies and can be used towards package holidays uk breaks and theme parks flights cruises hotels car hire airport parking insurance and much more client branded cardsloveshop gift cards can be personalised to reflect corporate identity or campaign theme  inline with other prepaid multioption cards on the market we can restrict the number of redeemers on the card for example restricting the card to clothing retailers only retailer vouchersin addition to the loveshop gift voucher and gift card we also offer a wide range of retailer vouchers and cards via loverewardcouk and highstreetvoucherscom  our loveshop extra gift card can also be used to buy other retailer vouchers hampers gifts  experiencesboth our corporate and consumer businesses offer a wide range of hampers gifts and experiences in addition to our voucher and card products park group plc   sitemapprivacy statementdisclaimer quick linksfinancial reports and accounts year summarydividend historyfinancial calendarshare price informationaim rule the boardcorporate governanceagm details designed  developed by emperor  wwwemperordesigncouk laminates foils  holographics for products  packaging  api  iconhome make an enquiry empowering brands™ to make a lasting impression to prosper to stand out to differentiate to make an impact to add value welcome to api api is a leading manufacturer and distributor of foils laminates and holographic materials which provide exceptional brand enhancement for consumer goods and printed media worldwide with roots in the british paper industry the company’s reputation is founded on a trading history going back over a century operating from thirteen locations across europe america and asia api’s packaging solutions enable companies across a widerange of industry sectors including premium 